$ git config --global user.name "ggoswami33"

to add anything into a branch
git init
git add .
git commit -m "comment message"
git push origin dev-branch


to merge the code into main branch from dev-branch
first go to main branch

git checkout main
then run the below command

git merge -m "commit message" source branch
git merge -m "commit message" dev-branch  -- its actually merging the code into main branch from dev-branch


to do the update branch
git update "update-git-for-windows"


to checkout any branch
git checkout main
git checkout dev-branch


to get the update from the current branch from remote branch
git merge origin/dev-branch
git merge origin/main